Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In a town with a long history, standing at the botton of a hill.\NWhere people go for education up and including university.\NPrivate school Seiohkan academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes that could not be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cute scool uniforms.\NLiberal scool philosophy.\NA campus with greenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that could never be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do those emotions go, once lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Minoru Hatsushima (Age 20) attends this campus\Nalong with his good friends,\Nand they're enjoying their\Ncarefree school life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki Katou (Age 20)   Naoya Kamata (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That which was clasped tightly\Nin their hearts were feelings of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya Futaki (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone other than myself", "My treasure".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something was forgotten somewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu Hatsushima (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they can't even remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru Hatsushima (Age 20)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost in feelings of anxiety...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Komomo Sakurai (Age 21)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they then remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your voice". "Your figure".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ungranted wishes never went anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were always, always right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, feelings of love will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The miracle of meeting you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, don't ever let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Episode 2: Promise\N"We will always be together..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem in high spirits today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}sky{\i0}-high!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you look so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What-could you have been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any strange dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Speaking of dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:03:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what kind of dream\Ndo you think I had last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an easy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it about rice cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've seen that one coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said the first thing\Nthat came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't get it,\NI {\i1}thought{\i0} it would be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to apologize for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night... I had\Na dream about you, Minoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dreamed about {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's why I couldn't wait\Nto see you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-chan, if we don't hurry up\Nand get to school, we'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Minoru and Senpai are {\i1}together{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good morning, Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Futaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-did you get lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you scored?\NYou got some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you even did {\i1}that{\i0}??
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT YOU SAY????
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you move so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some trick to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the first step!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you next time!\NNEXT TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I'm leaving Minoru in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Futaki-kun such a nice guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye for now, Minoru-chan.\NSee you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bye for now, Minoru-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the imitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called you "Minoru-{\i1}chan{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And is there something {\i1}wrong{\i0} with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not {\i1}exactly{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's older than I am,\Nso it's perfectly natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all. It's so nice\Nthat you get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm a little surprised that\Nyou captured Senpai's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm not saying you're not good\Nenough for her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}not{\i0} helping, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's better for her\Nthan you are, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you mean by {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I want you all\Nto myself, Naoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It looks like\Nsomething's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:06:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I owe a lot to Komomo-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't help but feel something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're referring to the age difference,\Nit's occurred to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody brought that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thought would never\Noccur to Komomo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it! She's probably thinking,\N"He's so cute, and sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rice cakes are delicious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you {\i1}ever{\i0} shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with Youko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko-chan, you can't keep on\Nacting like you did today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know full well what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're in a bad mood\Njust by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep that up, even my\Nbrother will be scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hatsushima say somethirfg to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What? Did I do something\Nto make her mad again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That Youko-chan is one straight arrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how he thinks of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can always tell when you're\Nfeeling down, Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Youko-chan, you have to say something\Nto him before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just what should I say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, do you really think that innocent\Nact is fooling anyone at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it really is too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought there'd be\Ncompetition for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just carried along, never making\Nanything clear, never being cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my fault for being complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use sneaky tricks to take my\Nbrother, there'll be hell to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be worrying about\Nyourself too, not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're up against Komomo-senpai\Nhere, and she's not to be taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother won't have any more\Ntime to dote on his kid sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an awful thing to say, Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can't keep my brother in the\Ndark about this any more than we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it eat away at you if he never\Nfinds out how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you were still\Nhanging around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was just talking\Nwith Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd ask if\Nwe could go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're walking home\Nwith Komomo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on! That's something\NAnzu would say, Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\N"Something {\i1}I{\i0} would say"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nishimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the fact\Nthat I like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just never learn\Nwhen to keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what are you {\i1}doing{\i0} to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't {\i1}mean{\i0} to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Komomo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about everything, Nishimura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Never mind, just go after her!\N- Never mind, just go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm meddling in his life even when\Nhe's already got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, will you treat me\Nto some comfort food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Youko-chan likes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was news to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, Minoru-chan, there\Nare cute girls all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you need me\Nwhen you've got them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, why are you\Nbringing that up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought you were my destined person\Nat the other end of the red string.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just because\NI'm not your soulmate, I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still looking only at you\Nwith everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are coincidences\Nmore important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, Minoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because now that I have you, Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing that Nishimura or even\NAnzu does will matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll lose my confidence\Nthat you're only looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} looking only at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot,\NMinoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... it's like I don't\Neven know you anymore!
