Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.04,0:25:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I liked you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.26,0:25:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.93,0:25:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about an answer for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.56,0:25:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.56,0:25:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rash, and did\Nsomething I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.74,0:25:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.99,0:26:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an impulse,\Nand I just went for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.28,0:26:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.37,0:26:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}said{\i0} it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.50,0:26:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that someday,\Nyou'll be able to accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.31,0:26:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sensei, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.52,0:26:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.33,0:26:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.29,0:26:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a hurry because\NI forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.33,0:26:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying attention, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.67,0:26:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not broken, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.55,0:26:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Main message\NLet's be together, 'kay!\NWait for me <3
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.30,0:26:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.76,0:26:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.02,0:26:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Please don't drop it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.94,0:27:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Minoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.74,0:27:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.91,0:27:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind from the east...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.34,0:27:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sounds like your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this big, big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.81,0:27:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under many, many clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.56,0:27:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.23,0:27:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things I wished for
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.62,0:27:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my heart racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you feel my excitement?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.05,0:28:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet again someday
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.39,0:28:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll keep drawing our own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.77,0:28:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings of love
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.23,0:28:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will never change
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.29,0:28:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.87,0:28:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you let go of me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.25,0:28:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to love you, so
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's take this first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.60,0:28:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stand on my tiptoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:28:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can I reach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.50,0:29:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To give you lots and lots of kisses
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lots and lots of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.88,0:29:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just too shy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.14,0:29:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep looking at me forever
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.44,0:29:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where we are
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.61,0:29:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the happiest guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this whole wide world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.17,0:29:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I could
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.38,0:29:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,meet with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.84,0:29:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.35,0:29:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new spark was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.77,0:29:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your frozen seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.78,0:29:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will start to change again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.93,0:30:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.10,0:30:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.61,0:30:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you let go of me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.11,0:30:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to love you, so
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's take this first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.54,0:30:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and start all over again.